name: Fast Food Vs. Aliens
blurb: Have you been waiting for another grid-based defense game to come out?  Check out Fast Food Vs. Aliens.

rewards.reward: For supporting us you will get a copy of the game when it is released for any one platform you want (PC, MAC, Unix. Android, iphone/ipad/itouch, xbox live)
Everything above plus a DRM free copy for all platforms mentioned above.
Beta Tester \u2013 Everything above plus as soon as playable version of the game is ready you will have access to download each version and test it out to help us refine the game for release.

Production Consultant \u2013 Everything above plus periodic access to production releases of the game.  Ability to play the production test versions and give feedback and you will receive a Production Consultant credit in the game and on the website.

Creative Consultant \u2013 Everything above plus access to art comps with ability to give feedback on art for the game, a signed limited edition poster and you will receive a Creative Consultant credit in the game and on the website (This credit supersedes all other credits \u2013 One credit per person).

Production Producer \u2013 Everything above plus access to current and past versions of the game and ability to give feedback at any part in the process.  Fast Food Vs. Aliens T-shirt.  You will receive a Production Producer credit in the game and on the website (This credit supersedes all other credits \u2013 One credit per person).  Please include $10 extra for shipping

Creative Director - Everything above plus 5  signed limited edition artwork prints from the game. You will receive a Creative Director credit in the game and on the website (This credit supersedes all other credits \u2013 One credit per person). Please include $10 extra for shipping

Creative Producer \u2013 Everything above plus as Creative Producer you will have exclusive input into the game.  You will also receive 10 limited edition signed prints of game artwork. Creative Producer credit in the game and on the website (This credit supersedes all other credits \u2013 One credit per person).

Project Producer \u2013 Everything above plus you will get 5 large giclee limited edition prints of game art, signed.  Project Producer credit in the game and on the website (This credit supersedes all other credits \u2013 One credit per person).

Executive Producer \u2013 Everything above plus we will design a character in the game based on you.  We will work off of a photo(s) you send us.  You will have final approval of the artwork.  You will also get the original artwork signed and framed.

Project Designer \u2013 Everything above plus 3 large signed original art pieces from the game which will be professionally framed as a one-piece triptych to archive quality specs. Project Designer credit in the game and on the website (This credit supersedes all other credits \u2013 One credit per person).
